     2→/**
     3→ * PulseLearn Campus Hub – Course Service
     4→ *
     5→ * A thin service-layer wrapper around all Course-related REST endpoints
     6→ * exposed by the Campus Hub API gateway.  Provides CRUD, enrollment,
     7→ * assignment upload, and real-time event subscription utilities.
     8→ *
     9→ * This file intentionally lives outside of React components so that
    10→ * business logic is co-located, testable, and reusable.
